## 🛠️ **Tools & Development Environment**

✅ **IDEs** – VS Code, PyCharm.  
✅ **Version Control** – Git + GitHub (`git clone`, `commit`, `push`, `pull`).  
✅ **Package Management** – `pip`, `poetry`, virtual environments (`venv`, `conda`).  
✅ **Debugging & Profiling** – `pdb`, `cProfile`, `memory_profiler`.

📌 **Bonus**: Learn **Docker, Kubernetes, and CI/CD pipelines** for deployment.

